Package: pedana
Title: A tool for creating pedigree problems and practicing pedigree analysis
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Justin",
           family = "Timm",
           email = "justin.timm@uni-due.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5718-3472"))
Description: 'pedana' is an R package which at its core provides a learning app 
    for practicing pedigree analysis. In addition, it provides the necessary 
    functions to simulate pedigree problems and to analyze and feedback 
    students' reasoning.
